<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sweet Ice - Heladería</title>

    <style>
        *{
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
            box-sizing:border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body{
            background:#fff0f5;
            color:#333;
        }

        header{
            background:linear-gradient(90deg,#ff69b4,#ffb6c1);
            padding:20px;
            text-align:center;
            color:white;
        }

        nav{
            margin-top:10px;
        }

        nav a{
            color:white;
            text-decoration:none;
            margin:0 15px;
            font-weight:bold;
        }

        .hero{
            height:400px;
            background:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1563805042-7684c019e1cb') center/cover;
            display:flex;
            justify-content:center;
            align-items:center;
            color:white;
            text-shadow:2px 2px 5px black;
            font-size:40px;
            font-weight:bold;
        }

        .container{
            width:90%;
            margin:auto;
            padding:40px 0;
        }

        h2{
            text-align:center;
            margin-bottom:30px;
            color:#ff1493;
        }

        .productos{
            display:grid;
            grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
            gap:20px;
        }

        .card{
            background:white;
            border-radius:15px;
            overflow:hidden;
            box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            transition:0.3s;
        }

        .card:hover{
            transform:scale(1.05);
        }

        .card img{
            width:100%;
            height:220px;
            object-fit:cover;
        }

        .card-content{
            padding:20px;
            text-align:center;
        }

        .precio{
            color:#ff1493;
            font-size:22px;
            font-weight:bold;
            margin:10px 0;
        }

        button{
            background:#ff1493;
            color:white;
            border:none;
            padding:10px 20px;
            border-radius:10px;
            cursor:pointer;
            transition:0.3s;
        }

        button:hover{
            background:#ff69b4;
        }

        footer{
            background:#ff69b4;
            color:white;
            text-align:center;
            padding:20px;
            margin-top:40px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>🍦 Sweet Ice Heladería</h1>

    <nav>
        <a href="#">Inicio</a>
        <a href="#">Sabores</a>
        <a href="#">Promociones</a>
        <a href="#">Contacto</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
    ¡Los mejores helados del mundo!
</section>

<div class="container">

    <h2>Nuestros Helados</h2>

    <div class="productos">

        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1570197788417-0e82375c9371" alt="">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Helado de Fresa</h3>
                <p>Delicioso helado artesanal sabor fresa.</p>
                <div class="precio">$3.00</div>
                <button>Comprar</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560008581-09826d1de69e" alt="">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Helado de Chocolate</h3>
                <p>Cremoso helado de chocolate premium.</p>
                <div class="precio">$4.00</div>
                <button>Comprar</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517093157656-b9eccef91cb1" alt="">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Helado de Vainilla</h3>
                <p>Suave y dulce sabor clásico de vainilla.</p>
                <div class="precio">$2.50</div>
                <button>Comprar</button>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 Sweet Ice Heladería | Todos los derechos reservados</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
